‚úÖ Import the AD Module

Import-Module ActiveDirectory

üßë‚Äçüíº Step 1: Create a New AD User

$Password = Read-Host "Enter password for the new user" -AsSecureString

New-ADUser `
  -Name "Oseme Vice" `
  -GivenName "Oseme" `
  -Surname "Vice" `
  -SamAccountName "o.vice" `
  -UserPrincipalName "o.vice@henryofcloud.com" `
  -AccountPassword (READ-Host -AsSecureString "@Cloudcomputing2025") `
  -Enabled $true `
  -DisplayName "John Doe" `
  -Path "OU=Sales,DC=henryofcloud,DC=com"

üß± Step 2: Create a New Security Group

New-ADGroup `
  -Name "Marketing" `
  -GroupScope Global `
  -GroupCategory Security `
  -Path "OU=Sales,DC=henryofcloud,DC=com"

‚ûï Step 3: Add User to the Security Group

Add-ADGroupMember `
  -Identity "Marketing" `
  **```(-Members "o.vice")**```

üîç Verify the Setup

Check user details:

Get-ADUser o.vice | Format-List Name,SamAccountName,Enabled

List members of the group:

Get-ADGroupMember Marketing

